obj_root_law_sections_1_content:
  string
  line 1
  line `THE AFRICAN DEVELOPMENT FUND ACT, 1982`
  line _________
  line `ARRANGEMENT OF SECTIONS`
  line ________
  line `S E CTIONS`
  line `1. Short title, extent and commencement.`
  line `2. Definitions.`
  line `3. Payments to Fund.`
  line `4. Reserve Bank to be depository for Fund.`
  line `5. Conferment of status and certain immunities, exemptions and privileges on Fund and conferment`
  line `of certain immunities, exemptions and privileges on its officers and employees.`
  line `6. Power to make rules.`
  line `7. Notifications issued under section 5 and rules made under section 6 to be laid before Parliament.`
  line `THE SCHEDULE.`
